Malingana ndi malamulo a chipani cha MCP, munthu amayenera kukhala pa mpando wa mtsogoleri wa chipani-chi kwa zaka khumi, ndipo potengera izi pofija mu 2025 President Lazarus Chakwera akhala kuti wamaliza zaka khumi zokhala pa udindo-wu.
